## Key Features
- Uses Pydantic v2 with ConfigDict(from_attributes=True) for ORM compatibility
- Field validations for answer choices (A/B/C/D), difficulty levels, SM-2 quality ratings
- Proper forward references using TYPE_CHECKING to avoid circular imports
- Comprehensive Field descriptions for API documentation
- Request/Response pattern for all API endpoints
